Text: "Argentina \U0001F1E6\U0001F1F7 is a magical country full of beautiful surprises.\
  \ Once you visit any of it\u2019s amazing cities and learn about it\u2019s fascinating\
  \ history, you\u2019ll want to go back again and again to feel the warmth of its\
  \ people, taste one of the best gastronomic experiences in the world, see the diversity\
  \ of Mother Nature masterpieces that feel this country, and learn how the Argentinians\
  \ know how to enjoy life. There is a big possibility of you wanting to live at this\
  \ unique and magnificent country."
